sentences: Cheapshot currently resides in Burbank, California.
From the mid-1990s to the late 2000s, Styles of Beyond was a pivotal force in the uprising of underground hip hop.
The group was later added to the lineup of Linkin Park's 2007 Projekt Revolution tour.
After years of touring and releasing records, the members of Styles of Beyond took an extended hiatus to pursue their own ventures.
